 6/3/16 . Got anoth all day pass , and went to Cario again . Spent the day in the citi , went to a show had a good time general . Back in camp at 11 P.M. 7/3/16 . Slip off to Heliopoli , and made myself comfort in the soldier club . Stay there all day ; came back to camp and was sit on my angerib ( a wicker bed ) when Sep walk in . Gosh ! I was pleas to see the priceless old feller . We went down into town and had a verit corrobborr . He had some grand tale of Gallipoli , and I am go over to his unit the , Camel Corp tomorrow . We have been camp within a mile of one anoth for near a month and did not know it .
